Pipeline Example

A shell script describing the pipeline can be found with the source code (see the "example/" folder). Here is an example of shell script which may be used to: 

Identify the Cells:

./PMTiffManip -f 2,4,6,8 HOwt_plate01_001006.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_red.tif 

./PMSegmentation -B 1.0f -b HOwt_plate01_001006_seg.scp -d HOwt_plate01_001006_dist.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_red.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_seg.tif

./PMFindMultiCover -o HOwt_plate01_001006_ellfit.mcv -c 1.0 6.0 -H3 HOwt_plate01_001006_tred.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_tsg.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_dst.tif

./PMWaterShed -M -b 1.0 HOwt_plate01_001006_red.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_watershed.tif

./PMHiddenMapDirect -M -G HOwt_plate01_001006_watershed.tif -C HOwt_plate01_001006_cellseg.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_seg.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_dist.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_ellfit.mcv

Measure GFP Intensity and spatial spread:


./PMTiffManip -f 1,3,5,7 HOwt_plate01_001006.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_gre.tif 

./PMExtractFeatures -m HOwt_plate01_001006_ellfit.mcv -a 0.9 0.1 10 50 -t HOwt_plate01_001006_feat_data.txt -S HOwt_plate01_001006_seg.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_red.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_gre.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_cellseg.tif

./PMMakeDisplay HOwt_plate01_001006_feat_data.txt HOwt_plate01_001006_cellseg.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_red.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_gre.tif HOwt_plate01_001006_preview.tif
